        {
            "title": "港股開市︱暫守兩萬六 恒指跌103點報26008點 友邦績後高開1.94%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股開市初段回吐，但暫仍守住兩萬六關。恒生指數開市報26008點，跌103點或0.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數開報4876點，跌33點或0.68%；國企指數以8757點開市，跌47點或0.54%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：友邦官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260319_FI_source-web_01299-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：友邦官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260319_FI_source-web_01299-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：友邦官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股跌多於升，滙控(00005)開報139.8元，跌0.85%；友邦(01299)今早公布首季業績後，股價在競價時段以86.6元開市，升1.94%。阿里巴巴(09988)開報128.2元，跌1.84%；騰訊(00700)開報474元，跌1.09%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國4大國有商業銀行均於昨天收市後派首季成績表，相關股份今早互有升跌。建設銀行(00939)開報9.04元，升0.56%；工商銀行(01398)開報7.13元，跌1.25%；農業銀行(01288)開報6.17元，暫時無升跌；中國銀行(03988)開報5.15元，跌0.58%，同系中銀香港(02388)開報44.08元，同樣暫時無升跌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國建設銀行2023年度年報\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250313_FI_source-web_00939.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國建設銀行2023年度年報\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250313_FI_source-web_00939.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國建設銀行2023年度年報</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國人壽(02628)亦於昨收市後公布首季業績，盈利倒退逾30%，但該股今早仍逆市再升4.02%，開報28.5元。昨天表現最佳藍籌中國海外(00688)於昨收市後派成績表，盈利跌27.5%，該股今早開報13元，回吐2.62。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15942027-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e6%9a%ab%e5%ae%88%e5%85%a9%e8%90%ac%e5%85%ad-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c103%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126008%e9%bb%9e-%e5%8f%8b%e9%82%a6%e7%b8%be%e5%be%8c%e9%ab%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-30 09:26:34",
            "source": "bastillepost",
