            "title": "山東黃金首季淨利升近41%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">山東黃金(01787)公布，截至3月31日，歸屬上市公司股東淨利潤14.46億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年升40.87%。基本每股收益0.29元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：山東黃金官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240712_FI_source-web_01787-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：山東黃金官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240712_FI_source-web_01787-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：山東黃金官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">扣除非經常項目淨利潤14.62億元，按年升41.94%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公布稱，淨利上升因生產運營管理能力提升，及黃金價格上漲 ; 營業收入升主要原因是自產金、外購金銷售價格均增加所致</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15941950-%e5%b1%b1%e6%9d%b1%e9%bb%83%e9%87%91%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e6%b7%a8%e5%88%a9%e5%8d%87%e8%bf%9141",
